<h2>Muhammad Ali</h2>
<p>🇺🇸 United States</p>

<h3>Record</h3>
<p>56 Wins - 5 Losses</p>
<p>37 Knockouts</p>

<h3>Championships</h3>
<p>🏆 3-Time Heavyweight Champion</p>

<h3>Style</h3>
<p>Speed, footwork, defense, psychological warfare</p>

<h3>Biography</h3>
<p>
Muhammad Ali is considered one of the greatest boxers in history.
He became heavyweight champion at age 22 and became known for his
speed, personality, and legendary fights.
